{
  "video_id": "0ztdofPc8Rw",
  "title": "Behind the lies of Holocaust denial | Deborah Lipstadt",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12902.0,
      "end_time": 16985.0,
      "text": "I come to you today to speak of liars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17900.0,
      "end_time": 18432.0,
      "text": "lawsuits"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18456.0,
      "end_time": 19796.0,
      "text": "and laughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20730.0,
      "end_time": 23840.0,
      "text": "The first time I heard about Holocaust denial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23864.0,
      "end_time": 25166.0,
      "text": "I laughed."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25790.0,
      "end_time": 27541.0,
      "text": "Holocaust denial?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28700.0,
      "end_time": 31437.0,
      "text": "The Holocaust which has the dubious distinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31461.0,
      "end_time": 35955.0,
      "text": "of being the best-documented genocide in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36866.0,
      "end_time": 38891.0,
      "text": "Who could believe it didn&#39;t happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39926.0,
      "end_time": 41273.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42770.0,
      "end_time": 44358.0,
      "text": "For deniers to be right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44382.0,
      "end_time": 46278.0,
      "text": "who would have to be wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46831.0,
      "end_time": 49597.0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, the victims --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49621.0,
      "end_time": 54338.0,
      "text": "the survivors who have told us their harrowing stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55541.0,
      "end_time": 57855.0,
      "text": "Who else would have to be wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57879.0,
      "end_time": 59832.0,
      "text": "The bystanders."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59856.0,
      "end_time": 63834.0,
      "text": "The people who lived in the myriads of towns and villages and cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63858.0,
      "end_time": 65830.0,
      "text": "on the Eastern front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65854.0,
      "end_time": 68295.0,
      "text": "who watched their neighbors be rounded up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68320.0,
      "end_time": 71532.0,
      "text": "men, women, children, young, old --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71557.0,
      "end_time": 74277.0,
      "text": "and be marched to the outskirts of the town"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74301.0,
      "end_time": 77293.0,
      "text": "to be shot and left dead in ditches."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77805.0,
      "end_time": 79135.0,
      "text": "Or the Poles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79159.0,
      "end_time": 83840.0,
      "text": "who lived in towns and villages around the death camps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83864.0,
      "end_time": 86240.0,
      "text": "who watched day after day"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86264.0,
      "end_time": 89600.0,
      "text": "as the trains went in filled with people"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89300.0,
      "end_time": 90553.0,
      "text": "and came out empty."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91607.0,
      "end_time": 95240.0,
      "text": "But above all, who would have to be wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95825.0,
      "end_time": 97289.0,
      "text": "The perpetrators."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97932.0,
      "end_time": 100838.0,
      "text": "The people who say, \"We did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101299.0,
      "end_time": 102823.0,
      "text": "I did it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102847.0,
      "end_time": 104996.0,
      "text": "Now, maybe they add a caveat."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105200.0,
      "end_time": 109444.0,
      "text": "They say, \"I didn&#39;t have a choice; I was forced to do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109924.0,
      "end_time": 112593.0,
      "text": "But nonetheless, they say, \"I did it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113758.0,
      "end_time": 115309.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115333.0,
      "end_time": 121271.0,
      "text": "In not one war crimes trial since the end of World War II"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121296.0,
      "end_time": 127932.0,
      "text": "has a perpetrator of any nationality ever said, \"It didn&#39;t happen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128898.0,
      "end_time": 133480.0,
      "text": "Again, they may have said, \"I was forced,\" but never that it didn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133504.0,
      "end_time": 134977.0,
      "text": "Having thought that through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135200.0,
      "end_time": 138953.0,
      "text": "I decided denial was not going to be on my agenda;"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138977.0,
      "end_time": 142685.0,
      "text": "I had bigger things to worry about, to write about, to research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142709.0,
      "end_time": 144230.0,
      "text": "and I moved on."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144731.0,
      "end_time": 147549.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward a little over a decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147574.0,
      "end_time": 149386.0,
      "text": "and two senior scholars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 149410.0,
      "end_time": 152567.0,
      "text": "two of the most prominent historians of the Holocaust --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152592.0,
      "end_time": 153849.0,
      "text": "approached me and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153873.0,
      "end_time": 155661.0,
      "text": "\"Deborah, let&#39;s have coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155686.0,
      "end_time": 159283.0,
      "text": "We have a research idea that we think is perfect for you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159307.0,
      "end_time": 163140.0,
      "text": "Intrigued and flattered that they came to me with an idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163164.0,
      "end_time": 164741.0,
      "text": "and thought me worthy of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164765.0,
      "end_time": 166861.0,
      "text": "I asked, \"What is it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167485.0,
      "end_time": 170474.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"Holocaust denial.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171173.0,
      "end_time": 173668.0,
      "text": "And for the second time, I laughed."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174156.0,
      "end_time": 176800.0,
      "text": "Holocaust denial?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176104.0,
      "end_time": 178900.0,
      "text": "The Flat Earth folks?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178114.0,
      "end_time": 180251.0,
      "text": "The Elvis-is-alive people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 180275.0,
      "end_time": 182463.0,
      "text": "I should study them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183146.0,
      "end_time": 184463.0,
      "text": "And these two guys said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184487.0,
      "end_time": 186420.0,
      "text": "\"Yeah, we&#39;re intrigued."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186832.0,
      "end_time": 188404.0,
      "text": "What are they about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188428.0,
      "end_time": 190178.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s their objective?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190202.0,
      "end_time": 193856.0,
      "text": "How do they manage to get people to believe what they say?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194576.0,
      "end_time": 198103.0,
      "text": "So thinking, if they thought it was worthwhile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 198128.0,
      "end_time": 201501.0,
      "text": "I would take a momentary diversion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 201526.0,
      "end_time": 204464.0,
      "text": "maybe a year, maybe two, three, maybe even four --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204488.0,
      "end_time": 206733.0,
      "text": "in academic terms, that&#39;s momentary."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206757.0,
      "end_time": 207899.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207923.0,
      "end_time": 210310.0,
      "text": "We work very slowly."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210334.0,
      "end_time": 211906.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211930.0,
      "end_time": 213732.0,
      "text": "And I would look at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213756.0,
      "end_time": 214911.0,
      "text": "So I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 214935.0,
      "end_time": 217774.0,
      "text": "I did my research, and I came up with a number of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217798.0,
      "end_time": 220391.0,
      "text": "two of which I&#39;d like to share with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 220415.0,
      "end_time": 221748.0,
      "text": "One:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221772.0,
      "end_time": 226728.0,
      "text": "deniers are wolves in sheep&#39;s clothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227532.0,
      "end_time": 230497.0,
      "text": "They are the same: Nazis, neo-Nazis --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230521.0,
      "end_time": 233748.0,
      "text": "you can decide whether you want to put a \"neo\" there or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234606.0,
      "end_time": 236939.0,
      "text": "But when I looked at them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236963.0,
      "end_time": 241689.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t see any SS-like uniforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 241713.0,
      "end_time": 244864.0,
      "text": "swastika-like symbols on the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 244888.0,
      "end_time": 246945.0,
      "text": "Sieg Heil salutes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 246969.0,
      "end_time": 248513.0,
      "text": "none of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 248537.0,
      "end_time": 251407.0,
      "text": "What I found instead"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 251431.0,
      "end_time": 256460.0,
      "text": "were people parading as respectable academics."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256736.0,
      "end_time": 257957.0,
      "text": "What did they have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 257981.0,
      "end_time": 259678.0,
      "text": "They had an institute."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 259702.0,
      "end_time": 263546.0,
      "text": "An \"Institute for Historical Review.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 264212.0,
      "end_time": 266765.0,
      "text": "They had a journal -- a slick journal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 266790.0,
      "end_time": 269744.0,
      "text": "a \"Journal of Historical Review.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270218.0,
      "end_time": 272924.0,
      "text": "One filled with papers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 272948.0,
      "end_time": 274991.0,
      "text": "footnote-laden papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275743.0,
      "end_time": 277683.0,
      "text": "And they had a new name."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 278320.0,
      "end_time": 280488.0,
      "text": "Not neo-Nazis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280512.0,
      "end_time": 283200.0,
      "text": "not anti-Semites --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 284284.0,
      "text": "revisionists."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284811.0,
      "end_time": 287250.0,
      "text": "They said, \"We are revisionists."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 287500.0,
      "end_time": 289733.0,
      "text": "We are out to do one thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 289757.0,
      "end_time": 293317.0,
      "text": "to revise mistakes in history.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294189.0,
      "end_time": 299599.0,
      "text": "But all you had to do was go one inch below the surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 299623.0,
      "end_time": 301530.0,
      "text": "and what did you find there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 301554.0,
      "end_time": 304440.0,
      "text": "The same adulation of Hitler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304680.0,
      "end_time": 305943.0,
      "text": "praise of the Third Reich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 305967.0,
      "end_time": 308909.0,
      "text": "anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 309724.0,
      "end_time": 312170.0,
      "text": "This is what intrigued me."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 312194.0,
      "end_time": 319191.0,
      "text": "It was anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice, parading as rational discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 320550.0,
      "end_time": 322137.0,
      "text": "The other thing I found --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 322161.0,
      "end_time": 325906.0,
      "text": "many of us have been taught to think there are facts and there are opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 325930.0,
      "end_time": 327386.0,
      "text": "after studying deniers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 327410.0,
      "end_time": 328746.0,
      "text": "I think differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 329258.0,
      "end_time": 330906.0,
      "text": "There are facts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330930.0,
      "end_time": 332644.0,
      "text": "there are opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 332668.0,
      "end_time": 334280.0,
      "text": "and there are lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 334969.0,
      "end_time": 339395.0,
      "text": "And what deniers want to do is take their lies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 340385.0,
      "end_time": 342170.0,
      "text": "dress them up as opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 342410.0,
      "end_time": 344310.0,
      "text": "maybe edgy opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 344550.0,
      "end_time": 346764.0,
      "text": "maybe sort of out-of-the-box opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 346788.0,
      "end_time": 348172.0,
      "text": "but then if they&#39;re opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 348196.0,
      "end_time": 350328.0,
      "text": "they should be part of the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 350352.0,
      "end_time": 353744.0,
      "text": "And then they encroach on the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 355125.0,
      "end_time": 356688.0,
      "text": "I published my work --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 356712.0,
      "end_time": 357885.0,
      "text": "the book was published,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 357910.0,
      "end_time": 361312.0,
      "text": "\"Denying the Holocaust: The Growing Assault on Truth and Memory,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 361336.0,
      "end_time": 363292.0,
      "text": "it came out in many different countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363316.0,
      "end_time": 365476.0,
      "text": "including here in Penguin UK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365500.0,
      "end_time": 368930.0,
      "text": "and I was done with those folks and ready to move on."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 369983.0,
      "end_time": 373691.0,
      "text": "Then came the letter from Penguin UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 374254.0,
      "end_time": 377220.0,
      "text": "And for the third time, I laughed ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 378908.0,
      "end_time": 380148.0,
      "text": "mistakenly."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 380792.0,
      "end_time": 382522.0,
      "text": "I opened the letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 382546.0,
      "end_time": 388433.0,
      "text": "and it informed me that David Irving was bringing a libel suit against me"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 388458.0,
      "end_time": 390550.0,
      "text": "in the United Kingdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 390790.0,
      "end_time": 393115.0,
      "text": "for calling him a Holocaust denier."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 393773.0,
      "end_time": 395707.0,
      "text": "David Irving suing me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 395731.0,
      "end_time": 396935.0,
      "text": "Who was David Irving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 396959.0,
      "end_time": 399566.0,
      "text": "David Irving was a writer of historical works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 399590.0,
      "end_time": 401613.0,
      "text": "most of them about World War II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 401637.0,
      "end_time": 404856.0,
      "text": "and virtually all of those works took the position"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 404880.0,
      "end_time": 408457.0,
      "text": "that the Nazis were really not so bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 408482.0,
      "end_time": 411566.0,
      "text": "and the Allies were really not so good."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 411590.0,
      "end_time": 413695.0,
      "text": "And the Jews, whatever happened to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 413719.0,
      "end_time": 415290.0,
      "text": "they sort of deserved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 417517.0,
      "text": "He knew the documents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 417541.0,
      "end_time": 418984.0,
      "text": "he knew the facts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 419800.0,
      "end_time": 422180.0,
      "text": "but he somehow twisted them to get this opinion."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 422836.0,
      "end_time": 425348.0,
      "text": "He hadn&#39;t always been a Holocaust denier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 425372.0,
      "end_time": 427113.0,
      "text": "but in the late &#39;80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 427137.0,
      "end_time": 429564.0,
      "text": "he embraced it with great vigor."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 431337.0,
      "end_time": 435241.0,
      "text": "The reason I laughed also was this was a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 435266.0,
      "end_time": 437200.0,
      "text": "who not only was a Holocaust denier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 437224.0,
      "end_time": 438919.0,
      "text": "but seemed quite proud of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 438943.0,
      "end_time": 440567.0,
      "text": "Here was a man -- and I quote --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 440591.0,
      "end_time": 444285.0,
      "text": "who said, \"I&#39;m going to sink the battleship Auschwitz.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 445165.0,
      "end_time": 446337.0,
      "text": "Here was a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 446361.0,
      "end_time": 450381.0,
      "text": "who pointed to the number tattooed on a survivor&#39;s arm and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 451536.0,
      "end_time": 453128.0,
      "text": "\"How much money have you made"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 453152.0,
      "end_time": 456551.0,
      "text": "from having that number tattooed on your arm?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 457369.0,
      "end_time": 459277.0,
      "text": "Here was a man who said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 459301.0,
      "end_time": 462257.0,
      "text": "\"More people died in Senator Kennedy&#39;s car"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 462281.0,
      "end_time": 463593.0,
      "text": "at Chappaquiddick"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 463617.0,
      "end_time": 466931.0,
      "text": "than died in gas chambers at Auschwitz.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 466955.0,
      "end_time": 469792.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an American reference, but you can look it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 471226.0,
      "end_time": 474240.0,
      "text": "This was not a man who seemed at all ashamed or reticent"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 474264.0,
      "end_time": 476333.0,
      "text": "about being a Holocaust denier."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 476956.0,
      "end_time": 480736.0,
      "text": "Now, lots of my academic colleagues counseled me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 480760.0,
      "end_time": 482666.0,
      "text": "\"Eh, Deborah, just ignore it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 482690.0,
      "end_time": 486278.0,
      "text": "When I explained you can&#39;t just ignore a libel suit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 486302.0,
      "end_time": 489840.0,
      "text": "they said, \"Who&#39;s going to believe him anyway?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 489603.0,
      "end_time": 491683.0,
      "text": "But here was the problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 491707.0,
      "end_time": 497150.0,
      "text": "British law put the onus, put the burden of proof on me"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 497390.0,
      "end_time": 499721.0,
      "text": "to prove the truth of what I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 499745.0,
      "end_time": 502508.0,
      "text": "in contrast to as it would have been in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 502532.0,
      "end_time": 504360.0,
      "text": "and in many other countries:"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 504600.0,
      "end_time": 507660.0,
      "text": "on him to prove the falsehood."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 507741.0,
      "end_time": 509202.0,
      "text": "What did that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 509226.0,
      "end_time": 512602.0,
      "text": "That meant if I didn&#39;t fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 512626.0,
      "end_time": 515520.0,
      "text": "he would win by default."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 515611.0,
      "end_time": 517366.0,
      "text": "And if he won by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 517390.0,
      "end_time": 520300.0,
      "text": "he could then legitimately say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 520539.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525391.0,
      "text": "\"My David Irving version of the Holocaust is a legitimate version."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 525415.0,
      "end_time": 527598.0,
      "text": "Deborah Lipstadt was found to have libeled me"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 527623.0,
      "end_time": 529570.0,
      "text": "when she called me a Holocaust denier."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 529594.0,
      "end_time": 534220.0,
      "text": "Ipso facto, I, David Irving, am not a Holocaust denier.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 534460.0,
      "end_time": 535758.0,
      "text": "And what is that version?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 536251.0,
      "end_time": 539247.0,
      "text": "There was no plan to murder the Jews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 539271.0,
      "end_time": 541323.0,
      "text": "there were no gas chambers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 541347.0,
      "end_time": 543203.0,
      "text": "there were no mass shootings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 543227.0,
      "end_time": 546398.0,
      "text": "Hitler had nothing to do with any suffering that went on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 546422.0,
      "end_time": 550227.0,
      "text": "and the Jews have made this all up"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 550251.0,
      "end_time": 552649.0,
      "text": "to get money from Germany"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 552673.0,
      "end_time": 554380.0,
      "text": "and to get a state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 554404.0,
      "end_time": 557781.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve done it with the aid and abettance of the Allies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 557805.0,
      "end_time": 561270.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve planted the documents and planted the evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 562280.0,
      "end_time": 564660.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t let that stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 564684.0,
      "end_time": 566884.0,
      "text": "and ever face a survivor"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 567643.0,
      "end_time": 569618.0,
      "text": "or a child of survivors."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 569642.0,
      "end_time": 571794.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t let that stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 571818.0,
      "end_time": 576690.0,
      "text": "and consider myself a responsible historian."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 577700.0,
      "end_time": 578752.0,
      "text": "So we fought."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 578776.0,
      "end_time": 581580.0,
      "text": "And for those of you who haven&#39;t seen \"Denial,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 581820.0,
      "end_time": 582241.0,
      "text": "spoiler alert:"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 582265.0,
      "end_time": 583483.0,
      "text": "we won."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 583507.0,
      "end_time": 584801.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 584826.0,
      "end_time": 587393.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 591808.0,
      "end_time": 596490.0,
      "text": "The judge found David Irving"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 596730.0,
      "end_time": 599404.0,
      "text": "to be a liar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 599428.0,
      "end_time": 600591.0,
      "text": "a racist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 600615.0,
      "end_time": 601869.0,
      "text": "an anti-Semite."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 601893.0,
      "end_time": 604253.0,
      "text": "His view of history was tendentious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 604277.0,
      "end_time": 606203.0,
      "text": "he lied, he distorted --"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 606227.0,
      "end_time": 608870.0,
      "text": "and most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 608894.0,
      "end_time": 611700.0,
      "text": "he did it deliberately."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 611310.0,
      "end_time": 615170.0,
      "text": "We showed a pattern, in over 25 different major instances."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 615194.0,
      "end_time": 618304.0,
      "text": "Not small things -- many of us in this audience write books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 618328.0,
      "end_time": 619512.0,
      "text": "are writing books;"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 619537.0,
      "end_time": 623300.0,
      "text": "we always make mistakes, that&#39;s why we&#39;re glad to have second editions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 623270.0,
      "end_time": 624213.0,
      "text": "correct the mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 624237.0,
      "end_time": 625387.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 626454.0,
      "end_time": 629589.0,
      "text": "But these always moved in the same direction:"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 630438.0,
      "end_time": 632649.0,
      "text": "blame the Jews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 632673.0,
      "end_time": 634848.0,
      "text": "exonerate the Nazis."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 635520.0,
      "end_time": 637103.0,
      "text": "But how did we win?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 638160.0,
      "end_time": 643396.0,
      "text": "What we did is follow his footnotes back to his sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 644100.0,
      "end_time": 645793.0,
      "text": "And what did we find?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 645817.0,
      "end_time": 647296.0,
      "text": "Not in most cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 647320.0,
      "end_time": 649288.0,
      "text": "and not in the preponderance of cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 649312.0,
      "end_time": 653623.0,
      "text": "but in every single instance where he made some reference to the Holocaust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 653647.0,
      "end_time": 657889.0,
      "text": "that his supposed evidence was distorted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 657913.0,
      "end_time": 659333.0,
      "text": "half-truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 659357.0,
      "end_time": 660690.0,
      "text": "date-changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 660715.0,
      "end_time": 662902.0,
      "text": "sequence-changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 662926.0,
      "end_time": 665500.0,
      "text": "someone put at a meeting who wasn&#39;t there."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 665740.0,
      "end_time": 667834.0,
      "text": "In other words, he didn&#39;t have the evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 667859.0,
      "end_time": 669968.0,
      "text": "His evidence didn&#39;t prove it."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 669992.0,
      "end_time": 672651.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t prove what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 673448.0,
      "end_time": 675947.0,
      "text": "We proved that what he said happened --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 675971.0,
      "end_time": 678831.0,
      "text": "and by extension, all deniers, because he either quotes them"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 678855.0,
      "end_time": 681326.0,
      "text": "or they get their arguments from him --"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 681350.0,
      "end_time": 682596.0,
      "text": "is not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 682620.0,
      "end_time": 683809.0,
      "text": "What they claim --"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 683833.0,
      "end_time": 686454.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t have the evidence to prove it."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 688429.0,
      "end_time": 693173.0,
      "text": "So why is my story more than just the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 693197.0,
      "end_time": 697400.0,
      "text": "of a quirky, long, six-year, difficult lawsuit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 697280.0,
      "end_time": 702170.0,
      "text": "an American professor being dragged into a courtroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 702410.0,
      "end_time": 705850.0,
      "text": "by a man that the court declared in its judgment"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 705109.0,
      "end_time": 707359.0,
      "text": "was a neo-Nazi polemicist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 707383.0,
      "end_time": 709166.0,
      "text": "What message does it have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 709620.0,
      "end_time": 712593.0,
      "text": "I think in the context of the question of truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 712617.0,
      "end_time": 715790.0,
      "text": "it has a very significant message."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 715103.0,
      "end_time": 716887.0,
      "text": "Because today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 716912.0,
      "end_time": 718578.0,
      "text": "as we well know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 718602.0,
      "end_time": 722718.0,
      "text": "truth and facts are under assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 723522.0,
      "end_time": 726774.0,
      "text": "Social media, for all the gifts it has given us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 726798.0,
      "end_time": 732379.0,
      "text": "has also allowed the difference between facts -- established facts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 732403.0,
      "end_time": 734160.0,
      "text": "and lies"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 734184.0,
      "end_time": 735582.0,
      "text": "to be flattened."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 736810.0,
      "end_time": 738319.0,
      "text": "Third of all:"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 738344.0,
      "end_time": 739815.0,
      "text": "extremism."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 740807.0,
      "end_time": 744384.0,
      "text": "You may not see Ku Klux Klan robes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 744408.0,
      "end_time": 746479.0,
      "text": "you may not see burning crosses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 746503.0,
      "end_time": 750822.0,
      "text": "you may not even hear outright white supremacist language."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 750846.0,
      "end_time": 755752.0,
      "text": "It may go by names: \"alt-right,\" \"National Front\" -- pick your names."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 755776.0,
      "end_time": 761611.0,
      "text": "But underneath, it&#39;s that same extremism that I found in Holocaust denial"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 761635.0,
      "end_time": 765290.0,
      "text": "parading as rational discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 766954.0,
      "end_time": 772170.0,
      "text": "We live in an age where truth is on the defensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 772195.0,
      "end_time": 774679.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m reminded of a New Yorker cartoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 774703.0,
      "end_time": 777223.0,
      "text": "A quiz show recently appeared in \"The New Yorker\""
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 777247.0,
      "end_time": 780468.0,
      "text": "where the host of the quiz show is saying to one of the contestants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 780493.0,
      "end_time": 782802.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, ma&#39;am, you had the right answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 782826.0,
      "end_time": 785319.0,
      "text": "But your opponent yelled more loudly than you did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 785343.0,
      "end_time": 786867.0,
      "text": "so he gets the point.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 788480.0,
      "end_time": 789555.0,
      "text": "What can we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 790377.0,
      "end_time": 791753.0,
      "text": "First of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 791778.0,
      "end_time": 797209.0,
      "text": "we cannot be beguiled by rational appearances."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 797233.0,
      "end_time": 799200.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got to look underneath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 799260.0,
      "end_time": 801827.0,
      "text": "and we will find there the extremism."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 802811.0,
      "end_time": 804797.0,
      "text": "Second of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 804821.0,
      "end_time": 810902.0,
      "text": "we must understand that truth is not relative."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 812957.0,
      "end_time": 814421.0,
      "text": "Number three,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 814445.0,
      "end_time": 818134.0,
      "text": "we must go on the offensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 818158.0,
      "end_time": 819931.0,
      "text": "not the defensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 820496.0,
      "end_time": 823103.0,
      "text": "When someone makes an outrageous claim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 823127.0,
      "end_time": 826631.0,
      "text": "even though they may hold one of the highest offices in the land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 826655.0,
      "end_time": 828665.0,
      "text": "if not the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 828690.0,
      "end_time": 830200.0,
      "text": "we must say to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 830224.0,
      "end_time": 832190.0,
      "text": "\"Where&#39;s the proof?"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 832214.0,
      "end_time": 834351.0,
      "text": "Where&#39;s the evidence?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 834375.0,
      "end_time": 837302.0,
      "text": "We must hold their feet to the fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 837326.0,
      "end_time": 841932.0,
      "text": "We must not treat it as if their lies are the same as the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 843215.0,
      "end_time": 846755.0,
      "text": "And as I said earlier, truth is not relative."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 846779.0,
      "end_time": 849635.0,
      "text": "Many of us have grown up in the world of the academy"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 849659.0,
      "end_time": 851400.0,
      "text": "and enlightened liberal thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 851424.0,
      "end_time": 854385.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;re taught everything is open to debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 854984.0,
      "end_time": 856998.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 857220.0,
      "end_time": 860464.0,
      "text": "There are certain things that are true."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 861120.0,
      "end_time": 864310.0,
      "text": "There are indisputable facts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 864560.0,
      "end_time": 865746.0,
      "text": "objective truths."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 866339.0,
      "end_time": 871156.0,
      "text": "Galileo taught it to us centuries ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 871180.0,
      "end_time": 875847.0,
      "text": "Even after being forced to recant by the Vatican"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 875871.0,
      "end_time": 878444.0,
      "text": "that the Earth moved around the Sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 878468.0,
      "end_time": 879622.0,
      "text": "he came out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 879646.0,
      "end_time": 881955.0,
      "text": "and what is he reported to have said?"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 881980.0,
      "end_time": 885802.0,
      "text": "\"And yet, it still moves.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 887162.0,
      "end_time": 890200.0,
      "text": "The Earth is not flat."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 890260.0,
      "end_time": 892315.0,
      "text": "The climate is changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 893207.0,
      "end_time": 895475.0,
      "text": "Elvis is not alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 895499.0,
      "end_time": 897340.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 897580.0,
      "end_time": 899374.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 899398.0,
      "end_time": 901699.0,
      "text": "And most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 901723.0,
      "end_time": 906372.0,
      "text": "truth and fact are under assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 907109.0,
      "end_time": 908719.0,
      "text": "The job ahead of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 908743.0,
      "end_time": 909946.0,
      "text": "the task ahead of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 909970.0,
      "end_time": 911564.0,
      "text": "the challenge ahead of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 911588.0,
      "end_time": 912822.0,
      "text": "is great."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 913567.0,
      "end_time": 916204.0,
      "text": "The time to fight is short."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 917610.0,
      "end_time": 919904.0,
      "text": "We must act now."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 920749.0,
      "end_time": 923994.0,
      "text": "Later will be too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 924180.0,
      "end_time": 925280.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 925304.0,
      "end_time": 929350.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}